key "SWAG"
literal "false"

\end_inset

.
 Hence, encouraging party densities below 10-100 parties/km
\begin_inset Formula $^{2}$
\end_inset

 
\emph on
in localized avalanche terrain
\emph default
 would be wise, and ten-times lower (intimated by Figure 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
