 The wording is important, but in the snow world, something akin to 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Hello Below!
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Skiing!
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

, and 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

